></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 351 1550 433 1598"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 440 1560 482 1599"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 491 1551 594 1594"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 603 1561 717 1599"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 726 1557 799 1593"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 808 1554 911 1599"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 920 1552 1052 1601"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1060 1552 1249 1601"></span>Prüfungsarbeit nicht zu Plären waren, oder ſofern wichtige Fertigkeiten</span><span class="ocr_line" title="bbox 91 1617 1250 1676"><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 91 1624 149 1661"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 153 1622 285 1676"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 289 1626 336 1659"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 338 1622 432 1665"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 435 1623 489 1660"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 492 1617 746 1667"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 746 1618 826 1665"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 828 1620 986 1667"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 987 1625 1107 1665"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1109 1622 1250 1666"></span>des Berufes an Hand der Prüfungsarbeit nicht überprüft werden konnten,</span><span class="ocr_line" title="bbox 91 1685 1249 1735"><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 91 1685 182 1728"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 189 1686 239 1728"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 246 1687 422 1732"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 430 1687 512 1727"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 518 1689 622 1733"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 625 1685 833 1732"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 841 1688 909 1728"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 917 1690 1064 1735"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1071 1691 1249 1734"></span>bietet die Vornahme einer ſogen. Arbeitsprobe eine geeignete Ergänzung</span><span class="ocr_line" title="bbox 92 1751 1249 1802"><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 92 1759 148 1796"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 151 1752 303 1801"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 308 1751 371 1794"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 375 1755 437 1800"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 441 1752 521 1801"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 525 1756 612 1801"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 615 1756 683 1801"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 687 1755 743 1795"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 747 1761 804 1800"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 807 1752 948 1802"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 951 1756 1135 1802"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1138 1756 1249 1799"></span>der Prüfung. Sie ſoll nicht mehr Zeit als zur Klärung notwendig, keines-</span><span class="ocr_line" title="bbox 92 1820 1249 1872"><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 92 1825 174 1869"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 190 1824 263 1864"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 278 1824 366 1868"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 375 1823 433 1862"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 446 1825 533 1864"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 543 1820 656 1869"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 667 1825 739 1869"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 748 1823 789 1868"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 790 1823 1044 1869"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1056 1825 1094 1864"></span><span class="ocrx_word" title="bbox 1100 1824 1249 1869"></span>falls aber mehr als einen halben Tag (4 Arbeitsſtunden) in Anſpruch</span></p>
